<paragraph id="6C1DDC927C9194F47E418C2D045662B4" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="846D238FF4220C34B7FC814D29F5EBB3" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Almost identical to 
<taxonomicName id="A1E676B923BE7A16FB8ECE3EC2FFF3C8" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomoea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="eggersiana">
